{"tha-ap339:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap339:0.2":"Gandhodakavagga ","tha-ap339:0.3":"Tinakutidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap339:1.1":"“Nagare bandhumatiya, ","tha-ap339:1.2":"ahosim parakammiko; ","tha-ap339:1.3":"Parakammayane yutto, ","tha-ap339:1.4":"parabhattam apassito. ","tha-ap339:2.1":"Rahogato nisiditva, ","tha-ap339:2.2":"evam cintesaham tada; ","tha-ap339:2.3":"Buddho loke samuppanno, ","tha-ap339:2.4":"adhikaro ca natthi me. ","tha-ap339:3.1":"Kalo me gatim sodhetum, ","tha-ap339:3.2":"khano me patipadito; ","tha-ap339:3.3":"Dukkho nirayasamphasso, ","tha-ap339:3.4":"apunnananhi paninam. ","tha-ap339:4.1":"Evaham cintayitvana, ","tha-ap339:4.2":"kammasamim upagamim; ","tha-ap339:4.3":"Ekaham kammam yacitva, ","tha-ap339:4.4":"vipinam pavisim aham. ","tha-ap339:5.1":"Tinakatthanca vallinca, ","tha-ap339:5.2":"aharitvanaham tada; ","tha-ap339:5.3":"Tidandake thapetvana, ","tha-ap339:5.4":"akam tinakutim aham. ","tha-ap339:6.1":"Sanghassatthaya kutikam, ","tha-ap339:6.2":"niyyadetvana tam aham; ","tha-ap339:6.3":"Tadaheyeva agantva, ","tha-ap339:6.4":"kammasamim upagamim. ","tha-ap339:7.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap339:7.2":"tavatimsamagacchaham; ","tha-ap339:7.3":"Tattha me sukatam byamham, ","tha-ap339:7.4":"kutikaya sunimmitam. ","tha-ap339:8.1":"Sahassakandam satabhendu, ","tha-ap339:8.2":"dhajalu haritamayam; ","tha-ap339:8.3":"Satasahassaniyyuha, ","tha-ap339:8.4":"byamhe patubhavimsu me. ","tha-ap339:9.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap339:9.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap339:9.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap339:9.4":"pasado upatitthati. ","tha-ap339:10.1":"Bhayam va chambhitattam va, ","tha-ap339:10.2":"lomahamso na vijjati; ","tha-ap339:10.3":"Tasam mama na janami, ","tha-ap339:10.4":"tinakutikayidam phalam. ","tha-ap339:11.1":"Sihabyaggha ca dipi ca, ","tha-ap339:11.2":"acchakokataracchaka; ","tha-ap339:11.3":"Sabbe mam parivajjenti, ","tha-ap339:11.4":"tinakutikayidam phalam. ","tha-ap339:12.1":"Sarisapa ca bhuta ca, ","tha-ap339:12.2":"ahi kumbhandarakkhasa; ","tha-ap339:12.3":"Tepi mam parivajjenti, ","tha-ap339:12.4":"tinakutikayidam phalam. ","tha-ap339:13.1":"Na papasupinassapi, ","tha-ap339:13.2":"sarami dassanam mama; ","tha-ap339:13.3":"Upatthita sati mayham, ","tha-ap339:13.4":"tinakutikayidam phalam. ","tha-ap339:14.1":"Tayeva tinakutikaya, ","tha-ap339:14.2":"anubhotvana sampada; ","tha-ap339:14.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap339:14.4":"dhammam sacchikarim aham. ","tha-ap339:15.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap339:15.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap339:15.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap339:15.4":"tinakutikayidam phalam. ","tha-ap339:16.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap339:16.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap339:16.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap339:17.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tinakutidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap339:18.1":"Tinakutidayakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}